/Question : What are two effective ways for the Scrum Team to make non-functional requirements visible ?
/Choose the two best answers :
/A) Add them to the definition of done so the work is taken care of every Sprint 
/B) Add them to the Product Backlog to ensure transparency 
/C) Put them on a separate list on the Scrum Board, Available for all to see
/D) Run the integration and regression tests before the end of the Sprint, and capture the open work For The Sprint Backlog of the next Sprint

AB